**Key concepts used:**

**Nested Switch-Case** — outer switch selects the artist, inner switch selects the mood.

**Structure:**
- Level 1 → Artist (1–5)
- Level 2 → Mood (Melody / Kuthu / Motivational / Sad)
- Each inner `case` prints the matching song list

**Note:** Harish Jeyaraj has no Motivational category as per your images, so only 3 moods are listed for him.
